they're all in the day.

00:17:39.510 --> 00:17:43.545
For 60 hunter-gatherer societies,
information on stories,

00:17:43.545 --> 00:17:47.645
songs, healing and
ceremonies is in the files,

00:17:47.645 --> 00:17:52.046
and of course as we all know,
we too hunt and gather stories

00:17:52.046 --> 00:17:56.940
through theater, film,
recording, literature,

00:17:56.940 --> 00:17:58.700
to feed our imaginations,

00:17:58.700 --> 00:18:03.330
I mean we really are
as addicted as anybody.

00:18:03.330 --> 00:18:08.018
